data.title: George Washington University: Costs, Jobs, Bar Results
data.meta_description: George Washington University overview on law school tuition, debt, salaries, enrollment, lawyer jobs, bar pass rates, and more. George Washington University currently enrolls a total of 1,679 students in their JD program. With an acceptance rate of 28.7%, they welcomed 521 new 1Ls in 2023 with a median LSAT of 168. Tuition and fees are $69.7k annually. Cost of living is estimated at $30.3k.
